-- Facebook CEO plans to grow headcount in 2013
-- 
-- Wed Jan 30, 2013 6:11pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/01/30/us-facebook-idUSBRE90T1HC20130130

 

 SAN FRANCISCO  (Reuters) - Facebook Inc CEO Mark Zuckerberg said the company expects to grow its headcount in 2013 as it invests in new products. Zuckerberg said the world's No.1 social network will be focused on building the business for the long-term and will not be operating to maximize profit in 2013. 
 (Reporting By Alexei Oreskovic)